   <conbody>
      <p>This section provides the procedures for configuring and assigning an <ph keyref="externalIdam"/> system for user authentication and authorization in <ph keyref="ECM"/>. By default, <ph keyref="ECM"/> is configured with ForgeRock
         OpenAM/OpenDJ for user authentication and authorization. Configuring an <ph keyref="externalIdam"/> is optional.</p>
